<emphasis bold="true" box="[86,239,2627,2652]" pageId="6" pageNumber="603">Bibliography.</emphasis>
Dollman (1911b, 1914), Dieterlen (2013f), Heller (1914), Hollister (1919), Janecek (1990), Monadjem et al. (2015), Musser &amp; Carleton (2005), Setzer (1975).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
