<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="603" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="6.[1360,2567,2814,3476]" pageId="6" pageNumber="603">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1361,1495,3408,3437]" pageId="6" pageNumber="603">Breeding.</emphasis>
Nguru Spiny Mice are most abundant during the wet season (February-March) in Tanzania.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
