<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="604" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="7.[174,1380,257,521]" pageId="7" pageNumber="604">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[176,529,374,403]" pageId="7" pageNumber="604">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not yet assessed on The IUCN Red List. Presence and abundance of the Nguru Spiny Mouse in cultivated areas and the buffer zone of Selous Game Reserve suggest that a classification of Least Concern could be appropriate.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
